---
title: "US55 — Admin password reset"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ForgotPasswordScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>RequestPasswordReset
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>User credentials (auth.users)
  A->>B: enter email, tap SEND RESET LINK
  B->>C: send(email)
  C->>E: resetPasswordForEmail(email)
  E-->>C: ok (no account disclosure)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (sent)
  B-->>A: "If an account exists, a reset link was sent."
  note over E: resetPasswordForEmail via AuthGateway → Supabase Auth.<br/>same confirmation regardless of account existence (anti-enumeration)
